{"tid":482040,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有兩部手提電腦要二揀一，想搵人俾吓意見","createTime":"2017-11-27T18:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T01:45:26.000Z","uid":57369,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"869e94e5b5d7d0b75035d8d0dfb5df75a41fa186","tid":482040,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:58:23.000Z","msg":"我呢排想買部手提電腦，睇啱兩部，但係唔知買邊部好，想搵人俾吓意見，部機只會用嚟做文書嘢<br />\n<br />\n兩部機都係差唔多價錢，CPU，ram，全部一樣，但係有以下少少分別<br />\n<br />\n電腦A 14寸Mon 12小時電量（佢話）<br />\n<br />\n電腦B 15.5寸Mon 9小時電量（佢話）<br />\n<br />\n邊部會好啲？"},{"pid":"3cdc1c05891199b5ac13c5c9980d470f05151b80","tid":482040,"uid":116530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:59:41.000Z","msg":"做文書嘢梗係要多電嗰部啦"},{"pid":"40defde4bd658c3a51cb3fd83763fb2d46f942b2","tid":482040,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:59:49.000Z","msg":"漏咗，我唔係次次用電腦嗰陣都會有插蘇可以充電"},{"pid":"2c5465e0bea490de25533fe92b689810d439f057","tid":482040,"uid":57369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T19:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做文書嘢梗係要多電嗰部啦</blockquote><br />\n嗰Mon 唔同size，會唔會有好大分別？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比較擔心呢樣"},{"pid":"fb9d23bf9f64c242e293353e10395690b57f1c10","tid":482040,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T19:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做文書嘢梗係要多電嗰部啦</blockquote><br />\n嗰Mon 唔同size，會唔會有好大分別？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比較擔心呢樣</blockquote><br />\n我覺得又唔係打機 細少少有咩所謂？"},{"pid":"553861df58b8c54096c72071e867dd2428cb5904","tid":482040,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T19:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做文書嘢梗係要多電嗰部啦</blockquote><br />\n嗰Mon 唔同size，會唔會有好大分別？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比較擔心呢樣</blockquote><br />\n我覺得又唔係打機 細少